---
---
<section class="py-24 bg-white border-y border-slate-100 relative overflow-hidden">

  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      
      <div>
        <div class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-[#0a2540]/10 bg-[#0a2540]/5 text-[#0a2540] text-sm font-bold mb-6">
          Who We Are
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold text-[#0a2540] mb-6 tracking-tight">
          Redefining Global <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-[#f97316] to-[#fdba74]">Mobility</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6 font-medium">
          At Travelpe, we don't just book flights—we engineer your entire international journey. By leveraging data-driven destination profiling and deep knowledge of global visa policies, we eliminate the friction of cross-border travel.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-8 font-medium">
          Whether you need a complex multi-country visa appointment or a fully tailored vacation package, our dedicated consultants operate as your personal travel architects.
        </p>
        
        <ul class="space-y-4">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-slate-700 font-bold">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#f97316]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
            Data-Backed Destination Matching
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-slate-700 font-bold">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#f97316]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
            Automated Visa Slot Tracking
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-slate-700 font-bold">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#f97316]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
            Premium End-to-End Itineraries
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Clean Travel Imagery -->
      <div class="relative group">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[#f97316]/10 translate-x-4 translate-y-4 rounded-[2.5rem] transition-transform duration-500 blur-md"></div>
        <div class="relative rounded-[2rem] overflow-hidden border border-slate-100 shadow-2xl bg-white">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1494522855154-9297ac14b55f?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1200" alt="Travel Airport Map" loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="w-full h-full object-cover aspect-[4/3] group-hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-700" />
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
